content.title: Add Sample User
content.body:
1. From the Data & Services panel on the top right of your canvas, expand Project Services.
  2. Right-click on UserAuthentication and select Edit. The Edit Identity Service window appears.
  3. Click Import Users. The Import Users window appears.
  4. Click Choose File. The window explorer appears.
  5. Navigate to the location of the exportUsers.csv file, select the file and click Open.
  6. Click Import.
  7. Close the Edit Identity Service window.
